    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/a031533bfa705fc5c53fcaf24e6901f5.poster.avif?t=1747692419\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/a031533bfa705fc5c53fcaf24e6901f5.webm?t=1747692419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/a031533bfa705fc5c53fcaf24e6901f5.mp4?t=1747692419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Put your feet up &amp; let your hair down, and spend some time filling an empty void with a vibrant little landscape. Biotopia aims to be a perfect companion while listening to a podcast or an audio book, with its addictive yet unobtrusive gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/80b2e8057d8930946fa06cae9da17a88.webp?t=1747692419\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/0cca6f5b530434422fe848e53f56dbc3.poster.avif?t=1747692419\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/0cca6f5b530434422fe848e53f56dbc3.webm?t=1747692419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/0cca6f5b530434422fe848e53f56dbc3.mp4?t=1747692419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Earn points by connecting tiles with similar biomes, and earn coveted <i>bonus tiles</i> by planning your placements carefully. Enjoy getting into the zone and staying there, plopping down pieces one by one and making the world grow.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/1cd39d5ea13cb3b149b2eeb6ec33ca92.webp?t=1747692419\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/a796fe0244f5beb44af98f3c4599e02f.avif?t=1747692419\" width=616 height=169 /></span><br>Diversity increases as your landscape expands, and new biomes will unlock when you reach certain milestones. All these can attract different kinds of wildlife; each with their own requirements and desires. Try finding them all, and complete the expansive ingame <i>biotopedia</i>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/68a9ec7762e1a97ee77860ab990ecee2.webp?t=1747692419\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Highscore mode</strong> if you want to challenge yourself and unlock a bunch of achievements.<br></li><li><strong>Endless mode</strong> if you prefer to relax and play in your own way without any failure states.<br></li><li><strong>Creative mode</strong> if you'd rather be a worldscaper and paint the world as you see fit.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363600/extras/639a6d1c2a1e68a5db5346618188808f.webp?t=1747692419\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br>Biotopia is under active development by a single person. If you have any questions, suggestions or feedback I would love to hear from you!<br><br>I'm putting together a demo ASAP, so <strong>wishlist</strong> and <strong>follow</strong> to get it as soon as it’s available! &lt;3",
